---
title: Creamy Green Chicken Breast, Veg and Pesto Pasta with Roasted Tomatoes
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Green Chicken Breast, Veg and Pesto Pasta in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
